result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  @ok="handleOk"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">

  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">

      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="开始时间">
      <a-date-picker showTime format="YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss"></a-date-picker>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="结束时间">
      <a-date-picker showTime format="YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss"></a-date-picker>
      </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
